A balanced state of energy/life energy 
=============================
First of all it should be very clear that any energy is neither is in balanced state of unbalanced state, it is the effect on which you say this energy is unbalanced or balanced.
If energy follow some order smoothly then their effect also come in smooth manner and we say this is balance state of energy and when the same state of energy stream quickly and its affect/destroy/harmful something then we used to say this is unbalanced state of energy.

***Energy/object/waves/nature always exists in state of streaming without any restriction/circumstance*** 

