Energy don't know this is life energy and this is non life energy, energy always are in state of streaming without any restriction. It is existence of nature. It is principle due to which each and every things get created/destroyed/streaming.

Energy never distinguish this is emotional/ thinking/ observation/fire/water/air/oil/understanding/realization/high intensity/low intensity/light intensity..so on. Energy have affinity for its stability who goes in hell and who goes in haven due to reaching their stability they never distinguish.

